\v 1 \add I am\add* \w Habakkuk|strong="H2265"\w*, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w prophet|strong="H5030"\w*. This \w is|strong="H5030"\w* \w the|strong="H2372"\w* \add message that Yahweh\add* gave \w to|strong="H5030"\w* me \w in|strong="H5030"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* vision.
